<title>zhǐ yǒu gàn kě de rén 迦南710</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 zhǐ yǒu gàn kě de rén cái zhī dào quán shuǐ de gān měi zhǐ yǒu jī è de rén, cái zhī dào wǔ gǔ de xiāng tián.
 zhǐ yǒu jiàn guò zhǔ de rén cái zhī dào shén me shì ài. cái néng pāo kāi shì shàng yī qiè de ài liàn.
 ō zhǔ nǐ de qiān bēi, ō zhǔ nǐ de shùn fú, ō zhǔ nǐ de shě jǐ, nǐ de wán quán.
 ō zhǔ yé sū, ō zhǔ yé sū, wǒ men yī tóng shì lì zài nǐ miàn qián.</lyrics>
</song>